<view class="page-shell--plain login-page">
  <view class="login-hero">
    <view class="login-logo">即</view>
    <view class="page-title">{{isEditing ? '编辑个人资料' : '登录即出'}}</view>
    <view class="page-subtitle">
      {{isEditing ? '更新你在校园交易中的展示资料' : '使用真实微信身份，完善你主动提供的资料'}}
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="surface-card login-card">
    <view wx:if="{{!showProfileForm && user}}" class="logged-in-panel">
      <image
        wx:if="{{user.avatarUrl}}"
        class="logged-avatar logged-avatar--image"
        src="{{user.avatarUrl}}"
        mode="aspectFill"
      />
      <view wx:else class="logged-avatar">{{user.avatarText}}</view>
      <view class="logged-copy">
        <text class="logged-title">当前已登录</text>
        <text class="logged-name">{{user.nickname}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view wx:else class="profile-form">
      <view class="field-label">头像</view>
      <button
        class="avatar-picker"
        open-type="chooseAvatar"
        disabled="{{isSubmitting || isReturning}}"
        bindchooseavatar="onChooseAvatar"
      >
        <image
          wx:if="{{avatarPreviewUrl}}"
          class="avatar-preview"
          src="{{avatarPreviewUrl}}"
          mode="aspectFill"
        />
        <view wx:else class="avatar-empty">
          <text class="avatar-empty-icon">＋</text>
          <text>选择头像</text>
        </view>
      </button>
      <text class="field-hint">由你主动选择，仅用于商品、主页和聊天展示</text>

      <view class="field-label field-label--spaced">昵称</view>
      <input
        class="profile-input"
        type="nickname"
        maxlength="20"
        value="{{nickname}}"
        placeholder="请输入 1～20 个字符"
        disabled="{{isSubmitting || isReturning}}"
        bindinput="onNicknameInput"
      />

      <view class="field-label field-label--spaced">
        校园信息
        <text class="optional-mark">选填</text>
      </view>
      <input
        class="profile-input"
        maxlength="40"
        value="{{campus}}"
        placeholder="例如：XX大学"
        disabled="{{isSubmitting || isReturning}}"
        bindinput="onCampusInput"
      />

      <view class="identity-note">
        微信身份由云端安全确认，昵称和头像不会被自动获取或伪造。
      </view>
    </view>

    <view wx:if="{{errorMessage}}" class="login-error">
      <text>{{errorMessage}}</text>
      <text
        wx:if="{{authStatus === 'error'}}"
        class="retry-link"
        bindtap="onRetryRestore"
      >
        重新校验
      </text>
    </view>

    <button
      wx:if="{{showProfileForm}}"
      class="wechat-login-button"
      loading="{{isSubmitting || isLoggingIn || isUpdatingProfile}}"
      disabled="{{isSubmitting || isLoggingIn || isUpdatingProfile || isReturning}}"
      bindtap="onLoginTap"
    >
      {{isSubmitting || isLoggingIn || isUpdatingProfile ? '正在保存' : (isEditing ? '保存资料' : '确认并登录')}}
    </button>

    <button
      wx:else
      class="wechat-login-button"
      disabled="{{isReturning}}"
      bindtap="continueAfterLogin"
    >
      {{isReturning ? '正在返回' : '继续'}}
    </button>

    <button class="back-button" bindtap="onBackTap">暂不操作，返回浏览</button>
  </view>

  <view class="privacy-note">
    头像、昵称和选填的校园信息仅用于校园二手交易中的展示与沟通。本页不申请手机号、通讯录或位置权限。
  </view>
</view>
